Welcome to the P1 *Technical Beta* of Wolcen: Lords of Mayhem!

The goal of this experimental Beta is to spot the major issues related to the Multiplayer implementation and how the servers are handling the game. The content is therefore limited to selected features in order to make a progressive testing.

P1 T-Beta will allow you to experiment the random dungeon with your friends and discover a portion of the new content we’re preparing for the Beta release.
 The servers will be opened starting October 18th until October 25th, 2018.

After that, we will close the servers and the technical Beta to work on bug fixing, and prepare for the Phase 2.

Don’t hesitate to join us on Discord and share your feedback with us!
https://discord.gg/wolcenstudio

<Font Size="13" >Thank you for joining the Beta of Wolcen: Lords of Mayhem!</Font>

The goal of this Early Access Beta is to allow you to test the game while we implement the final core elements and features through various patches.

Your help will allow us to spot the major issues and fix them as soon as possible. We plan to push regular hotfixes during this testing phase to improve your experience ingame so don't hesitate to report any issue you might encounter.

Your feedback also means a lot to us, so please let us know what you think of your game experience through the Official forums at wolcengame.com, or join us on Discord for a chat at discord.gg/wolcenstudio.

Finally, if you're enjoying the latest content, please consider giving us a review or updating your review on Steam. It's a great way to show your support, and it helps new players to know more about the game so our community can grow!

Have fun!
